{"tid":1133602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國要求三間中資銀行提交紀錄　涉違反制裁協議與朝鮮交易","createTime":"2019-05-01T07:49:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T11:30:47.000Z","uid":141151,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2d901a07f1fec1c6bfa74387537544bef2dda552","tid":1133602,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T07:49:39.000Z","msg":"美國要求三間中資銀行提交紀錄　涉違反制裁協議與朝鮮交易<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/323928/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E4%B8%89%E9%96%93%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%87%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84-%E6%B6%89%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0%E8%88%87%E6%9C%9D%E9%AE%AE%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F323928%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%2596%2593%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%25B3%2587%25E9%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%258F%2590%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E7%25B4%2580%25E9%258C%2584-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%258D%2594%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%259C%259D%25E9%25AE%25AE%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2598%2593&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEG9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=22626f58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/323928/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E4%B8%89%E9%96%93%E4%B8%AD%E8%B3%87%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84-%E6%B6%89%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0%E8%88%87%E6%9C%9D%E9%AE%AE%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93</a><br />\n<br />\n美國地區法院周二（4月30日）下令三家中資銀行，需交出涉嫌違反對朝鮮國際制裁的數千萬美元款項記錄，但有關文件並未公開涉事銀行名字。<br />\n<br />\n美國司法部周二（30日）公開一份在3月18日釋出的文件。華盛頓地區首席法官豪厄爾（Beryl Howell）表示，這傳票是關於香港一間已解散的公司，與朝鮮之間的交易紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n不過公開的文件部分內容被屏蔽，未有公開相關的香港公司或朝鮮團體的名字，同時未有公開經手交易三間銀行的名字，僅指該三家銀行均為中資。傳票要求銀行提供至2012年1月的各種銀行交易紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n2018年2月美國公布針對朝鮮新一輪制裁名單，當中涉及本港三間公司。事件揭露朝鮮透過香港設立境外公司，供匯款及洗黑錢之用。<br />\n<br />\n（路透社）"},{"pid":"69f51e669867b995524e93ef189f24f08a7d368c","tid":1133602,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T07:50:22.000Z","msg":"U.S. judge orders Chinese banks to hand over North Korea records<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-northkorea-usa-china-banks-idUSKCN1S62VU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-northkorea-usa-china-banks-idUSKCN1S62VU&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEG9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=2989087d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-northkorea-usa-china-banks-idUSKCN1S62VU&h=0f84e8da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-northkorea-usa-china-banks-idUSKCN1S62VU</a>"},{"pid":"26e85fc81bfe306081427df93b977546239fc5d4","tid":1133602,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T23:57:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff7560868dc878a34857311a168936c74fbb3ca1","tid":1133602,"uid":60057,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T01:03:58.000Z","msg":"好想美國快啲認清香港係中共白手套"},{"pid":"6dabb7a168f04a157fa1e00dfd930935b9a69b8c","tid":1133602,"uid":25673,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ff7560868dc878a34857311a168936c74fbb3ca1","tid":1133602,"uid":60057,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T01:03:58.000Z","msg":"好想美國快啲認清香港係中共白手套"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T02:33:24.000Z","msg":"一早知啦，香港只係未推出去既籌碼"},{"pid":"f822dfea0bff0ac944a82752f21cd0e19de87621","tid":1133602,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T02:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b3f8bdf12ed9b8d00cc779b5d157bd80881053d","tid":1133602,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201